\mbox{det}(A+I - xI) = \mbox{det}(A+(1-x)I)= \mbox{det} \left(  \begin{bmatrix} 1-x&0&0\\0&2-x&0\\0&0&x\end{bmatrix}\right) =x(1-x)(2-x) 
\chi_{A+I}(x)=\det(A+I-xI)=\det(A-(x-1)I)=\chi_A(x-1)
